ITEM 2.02.  RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
On April 26, 2010, Aarons, Inc. issued a press release to announce its financial results for the first quarter of 2010.  A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1.
ITEM 9.01.  FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS
