ITEM 2.02.  RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
On February 15, 2011, Aarons, Inc. issued a press release to announce its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year of 2010.  A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1.
