This Employee Agreement will be interpreted under and governed by the laws of the State of Georgia. Each party irrevocably (a) consents to the exclusive jurisdiction and venue of the state and superior courts of Fulton County, Georgia and federal courts in the Atlanta Division of the Northern District of Georgia, in any action arising under or relating to this Employee Agreement, and (b) waives any jurisdictional defenses (including personal jurisdiction and venue) to any such action.
