Non-Solicitation of Customers
(e) During employment and for a period of two years following the Termination Date, Executive will not solicit or attempt to solicit, directly or by assisting others, any employee, franchisee, or independent contractor to terminate his or her employment or other relationship with the Company. Notwithstanding the foregoing, nothing in this Section shall prohibit (i) general solicitations for employment and advertisements that are not specifically targeted towards employees of the Company, or (ii) using search firms that are not instructed to target employees of the Company.
