(b) . If the Company terminates Executive's employment for Cause, Executive shall be entitled to no payment or compensation whatsoever from the Company under this Agreement, other than accrued amounts as may be due him through his Termination Date, including Executive's Base Salary and any Earned Bonus through the Termination Date.
