This commitment expires fourteen (14) days following the date of this letter unless accepted below and returned to the Bank by that date. The Borrower understands that this commitment letter is being provided at the request of Aarons, Inc. pursuant to a loan program established for certain franchisees of Aarons, Inc. By acceptance of this Commitment Letter, the Borrower agrees to pay all legal fees and expenses incurred by the Bank in connection with the Line of Credit, regardless of whether the Line of Credit closes.
 
